          <para styleclass="Body Table"><image src="Red-14-3.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Parameter-Header"> Cam Start; </text><text styleclass="Body Text">Default = 0 : &#160;</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header"> &#160; &#160; Cam Range; </text> Default = 360</para>
