                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Interface2">Cam-Life</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> - (</text><text styleclass="SeeAlso">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-2DCam-CamLifetab" styleclass="SeeAlso">Cam Life</link><text styleclass="Body Text">) </text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">You can display the <text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Inner</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Interface2" style="color:#ff0000;">OR</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Outer</text> cam-profile, only - see <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-2DCam-DisplayTab" anchor="2DCAM-DIALOG-DISPLAY-VISIBILITIY">Display</link></para>
