      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Safety-Factor (Cam)</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName">Cam&apos;s Dynamic Max Contact-Stress = Max Contact-Stress × </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Safety-Factor (cam)</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Table" style="margin-bottom:0px;"><text styleclass="Interface2" style="color:#ff0000;">IMPORTANT NOTE: </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Interface2">Safety-Factor</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> (</text><text style="color:#ff0000;">Roller</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">)</text><text styleclass="VariableName"> =</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header"> Safety Factor (</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="color:#ff0000;">Cam</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">)</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:super; color:#ff0000;">2</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text"><equation styleclass="VariableName" font-size="32"><![CDATA[\therefore]]></equation><text styleclass="VariableName"> Roller&apos;s Dynamic Equivalent Load = Equivalent Load × </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Safety Factor (Cam)</text><text styleclass="Parameter" style="font-size:12pt; vertical-align:super; color:#ff0000;">2</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">E.g: If <text styleclass="Parameter">Safety-Factor (Cam)</text> = 1.1 ; &#160;<text styleclass="Interface">Safety-Factor (Roller) </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">= 1.21</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <para styleclass="Body Table">The <text styleclass="Parameter-Header">Safety Factor</text> should consider:</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">How the Cam-Shaft is driven - from a smooth, constant speed, servo-motor, to single-cylinder diesel engine.</para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">What the Cam-Follower drives - from a smoothly acting paper tucker, to a forging-press</para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The Stiffness, Rigidity, Inertia, Natural-Frequency, Backlash of the Payload relative to the Speed of the Cam</para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">The severity of the motion. </para>
                <para styleclass="Body Text">Backlash present in the driving system or the driven system.</para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
